<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-03-14T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-03-14T18:00:00-05:00" n="304" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d304">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/481</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SJH1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Shea</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-03-14T18:00:00-05:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">March 14, 1917, 6 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>You are instructed discreetly to investigate and report by cable upon
                                the activities of the Government of the Argentine Republic in <pb facs="0413" n="241" xml:id="pg_241"/> regard to bringing about
                                mediation by Latin-American powers, now that diplomatic relations
                                have been broken off between the United States and Germany. Also
                                report concerning the attitude of the Government to which you are
                                accredited in this connection and how reports have been received in
                                the country where you are located as to the activities of the
                                Argentine Government.</p>
                            <p>Repeat to Lima and Montevideo.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>